u hv hw es et paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="hx hy dj hz bg ia"><div class="es et hs"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*7CPIGOfQcS8d3RGFcufiiA.jpeg 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bg ib ic c" width="700" height="260" loading="eager" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div></figure><p id="4cb6" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja hc bj">Although January was a slow month for <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/5ed69ff9cfb0?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a>, The Hologram News Network (HNN) has been busy expanding into new areas of news content creation and distribution. Things have never looked brighter for HNN.</p><ul class=""><li id="a197" class="jd je hj if b ig ih ik il io jf is jg iw jh ja ji jj jk jl bj">Launched <a class="af jm" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDa-YxgNG6A9xpH1qyP0OaQ" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">The Hologram News Network Podcast</a> and <a class="af jm" rel="noopener" href="/the-hologram/introducing-the-holograms-create-and-earn-program-8c861aea892f?source=collection_detail----4d89daa6ae31-----24-----------------------">The Hologram’s Create And Earn Program</a></li><li id="a1d5" class="jd je hj if b ig jn ik jo io ho is hp iw hq ja ji jj jk jl bj">Onboarded 3 new Content Creators. Welcome <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/ad2a3faef607?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Sean Layton</a>, <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/2bfebca6a8e1?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">bee.bod</a>, and <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/b3ca146a7a78?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">JALLDIGITAL</a>!</li><li id="9b93" class="jd je hj if b ig jn ik jo io ho is hp iw hq ja ji jj jk jl bj">Built partnerships with Star Atlas guilds and content creators <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/800890c0705f?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Arktype</a> and <a class="jb jc gg" href="https://medium.com/u/a8563bab7fea?source=post_page-----3358d24a7c6f--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Star Dust Economy</a></li></ul><p id="d254" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja hc bj">In fact, January was our biggest month ever with 18 stories published. This is largely thanks to our new crew of talented creators.</p><figure class="jq jr js jt fe hw es et paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="hx hy dj hz bg ia"><div class="es et jp"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*k62LO6CcMeYgHpyyZUf6eg.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bg ib ic c" width="700" height="732" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="ju jv eu es et jw jx be b bf z dy">Hologram News Network Statistic for January</figcaption></figure><h1 id="fb21" class="jy jz hj be ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko kp kq kr ks kt ku kv bj">What to look for in February for HNN</h1><ul class=""><li id="63b8" class="jd je hj if b ig kw ik kx io ky is kz iw la ja ji jj jk jl bj">Exclusive lore interview with the Star Atlas lore master Jose</li><li id="da6a" class="jd je hj if b ig jn ik jo io ho is hp iw hq ja ji jj jk jl bj">Increased community outreach and marketing</li><li id="3cfd" class="jd je hj if b ig jn ik jo io ho is hp iw hq ja ji jj jk jl bj">New weekly podcasts and near-daily news coverage of Star Atlas</li><li id="0a5a" class="jd je hj if b ig jn ik jo io ho is hp iw hq ja ji jj jk jl bj">Community surprises for HNN 1 year anniversary in March</li></ul><h2 id="2736" class="lb jz hj be ka lc ld le ke lf lg lh ki io li lj lk is ll lm ln iw lo lp lq lr bj">HNN is here to inform and serve the Star Atlas Community</h2><p id="303d" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig kw ii ij ik kx im in io ls iq ir is lt iu iv iw lu iy iz ja hc bj">HNN empowers the SA community to create content. Whether you’re a beginner or seasoned creator, HNN will help you broadcast your message to Star Atlas’ most active and influential community members. At HNN, everyone’s voice matters. <a class="af jm" href="https://discord.gg/Jb5xjcGfwV" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Join us</a>!</p><p id="34f9" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja hc bj"><strong class="if hk">Want to be a part of the magic? We’re always looking to support talented creators in the field. Check out: </strong><a class="af jm" rel="noopener" href="/the-hologram/introducing-the-holograms-create-and-earn-program-8c861aea892f?source=collection_detail----4d89daa6ae31-----24-----------------------"><strong class="if hk">The Hologram’s Create And Earn Program</strong></a></p><p id="402d" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja hc bj"><strong class="if hk">Follow for Star Atlas News:</strong></p><p id="e889" class="pw-post-body-paragraph id ie hj if b ig ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja hc bj"><a class="af jm" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDa-YxgNG6A9xpH1qyP0OaQ" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">YouTube</a> | <a class="af jm" href="https://twitter.com/Hologram_News" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Twitter </a>| <a class=